data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Stunning Home in Desirable West Salem Neighborhood! Inviting front porch, Open Floor Plan, Vaulted Ceilings, and Abundant Windows create a light and bright home. The Heart of the Home, the Kitchen, features an Island, Walk-in Pantry, and Ample Cabinet Space. Expansive Deck offers City and Mountain Views, perfect for entertaining. Oversized Primary Suite features Double Doors, Large Bathroom with Double Sinks, and Walk-In Closet. New Carpet installed on 11/7. Additional amenities include UGS, drip syst., AC.
